title: Can Am Defender heavy duty tie rods 10 inches (2016 and 2017)
features: These heavy duty tie rods will replace the stock rods. (and look awesome!) 2016-2017 only

Fitment for the Can Am Defender only. Does not fit the MR10 model however. (See listings for other Can Am models) This is 10 inches long. If unsure of your size please measure your stock rods. You may also contact us if needing assistance.
Made from high strength 1 inch diameter 6061 aluminum (solid rod)
CNC machined, polished and then hard anodized for a perfect and long lasting finish
Direct bolt-on for easy installation. Available in black. If you are unsure which model to purchase please contact us.
description: Can Am Defender Heavy Duty Tie Rods will replace your weak stock tie rods! These are not only strong, they will also look great on your Defender! There is one model, the Defender MR10, that will not work . If you have a different Can Am please see our other listings.If you are unsure, please contact us and we are happy to help.
